high_descs: Walk forward, then hang a left and walk over to the small black table in between the couch and yellow chair.
Pick up the watch off of the small black table.
Turn left and walk up to the wall, then turn right to face the tall lamp.
Turn off the light of a tall lamp.
anns.task_desc: Turn off a lamp while holding a watch.

high_descs: Move to the small round table between the tan chair and the large red sofa
Pick up the watch on top of the small table
Carry the watch and move slightly left to face the large floor lamp
anns.task_desc: Hold a watch while turning off a lamp

high_descs: Take a step then turn left and walk to the chair then turn right and walk to the wall then turn right and walk to the small end table.
Pick up the watch that's on the end table.
Take a step to your left.
anns.task_desc: Inspect a watch by lamp light.
